Definition: eat food accompanied by lots of liquid
Example: also use metaphorically; She washed down her dinner with a bottle of red wine; He washes down his worries with a nightly glass of whisky
Synonyms: eat, food, accompanied, by, lots, of, liquid, also, use, metaphorically, She, washed, down, her, dinner, with, a, bottle, red, wine, He, washes, his, worries, nightly, glass, whisky
Frame: 8
Category: verb.consumption
